while looking at those architectures.

133
00:07:36,495 --> 00:07:37,724
That's true.

134
00:07:38,758 --> 00:07:40,776
This reminds me of those old days.

135
00:07:42,529 --> 00:07:44,130
Let's travel together again.

136
00:07:44,588 --> 00:07:45,604
Yeah.

137
00:07:46,677 --> 00:07:48,913
I won't be bored if I go with you.

138
00:07:52,312 --> 00:07:53,707
But I don't know when.

139
00:07:53,916 --> 00:07:55,834
It could be years from now.

140
00:07:56,631 --> 00:07:58,202
That long?

141
