How was it?

142
00:08:02,130 --> 00:08:05,266
It lives up to the name
of a state-of-the-art research university.

143
00:08:05,821 --> 00:08:08,021
Their joint research with foreign countries
is very interesting.

144
00:08:08,167 --> 00:08:09,210
