222
00:12:47,891 --> 00:12:49,435
to a dark place like this.

223
00:13:04,458 --> 00:13:05,499
Minato-san.

224
00:13:07,709 --> 00:13:08,988
Shin.

225
00:13:10,145 --> 00:13:11,180
