(Next Episode)

371
00:24:45,703 --> 00:24:47,453
(The summary of love beyond ages)
My feeling for him...

372
00:24:47,477 --> 00:24:49,160
(The summary of love beyond ages)
My feelings for Shin...

373
00:24:49,185 --> 00:24:51,023
(Lie to yourself, or be honest)
Shin's already leaving today.

374
00:24:51,047 --> 00:24:51,889
Are you sure about this?

375
00:24:51,913 --> 00:24:53,208
Minato-san.

376
00:24:53,232 --> 00:24:54,511
(A sudden farewell)
Here.

377
00:24:54,535 --> 00:24:56,061
(The letter)
Recipient.

378
00:24:56,177 --> 00:24:57,429
Minato Akira-san.

379
00:24:58,393 --> 00:24:59,415
Shin!

380
